monk: Me and the fam just got back from slaying another ancient being.
monk: Punch 'im? What kind of monster do I look like?
monk: We got 'im with the power of friendship!
if {HasMonkToken} == 0:
	monk: An autograph? I'm sorry, but I can't unclench my mighty fists.
	monk: Here. Have one of these instead. May your little robot arms be strong.
	[signal arg="coin_received"]
	set {HasMonkToken} = 1
	set {TokenCount} += 1
